# ============================================================
# EmailJS — Contact form se messages aapke Gmail par bhejne ke liye
# ============================================================
# 1) https://www.emailjs.com/ par free account banayein
# 2) Email Services → Add New Service → Gmail choose karein → apna Gmail connect karein
#    (jis inbox par messages chahiye, e.g. jhap54862@gmail.com)
# 3) Email Templates → Create Template:
#    - "To Email" / recipient: apna Gmail (ya service default)
#    - Subject: {{subject}}
#    - Content mein ye variables use karein (form ke name se match):
#        {{from_name}}, {{from_email}}, {{subject}}, {{message}}
#    - Optional: Reply To = {{from_email}} taaki Reply se visitor ko email jaye
# 4) Account → General → Public Key copy karein
# 5) Is file ko copy karke ".env" naam se project root mein save karein aur values bharein:
#
# VITE_EMAILJS_PUBLIC_KEY=your_public_key
# VITE_EMAILJS_SERVICE_ID=your_service_id
# VITE_EMAILJS_TEMPLATE_ID=your_template_id
#
# 6) npm run dev dubara chalayein (Vite env variables load karne ke liye)
# ============================================================

VITE_EMAILJS_PUBLIC_KEY=
VITE_EMAILJS_SERVICE_ID=
VITE_EMAILJS_TEMPLATE_ID=
